Name: Eat Lead: The Return of Matt Hazard

Achievements.Name: It's HAZARD TIME!
Achievements.Description: Start your first game.

Achievements.Name: Take 5.
Achievements.Description: Pause the game for the first time.

Achievements.Name: Straight-A Student
Achievements.Description: Complete all of the in-game tutorials.

Achievements.Name: Hands-On Approach
Achievements.Description: Defeat an enemy using melee combat.

Achievements.Name: Eat FIST!
Achievements.Description: Perform 10 single-hit melee kills.

Achievements.Name: Feeling Punchy
Achievements.Description: Defeat five enemies in a row using melee combat.

Achievements.Name: Headache
Achievements.Description: Score 20 headshots.

Achievements.Name: Migraine
Achievements.Description: Score 50 headshots.

Achievements.Name: Head of the Class
Achievements.Description: Score 100 headshots.

Achievements.Name: Better than One
Achievements.Description: Score two headshots with one bullet.

Achievements.Name: Plink
Achievements.Description: Kill 50 enemies with the Hazard pistol.

Achievements.Name: Pull!
Achievements.Description: Kill 50 enemies with the shotgun.

Achievements.Name: Auto Dealer
Achievements.Description: Kill 50 enemies with the sub-machinegun.

Achievements.Name: Russian Attack
Achievements.Description: Kill 50 enemies with the AK-47.

Achievements.Name: Peekaboo...I Shot You!
Achievements.Description: Kill 50 enemies with the sniper rifle.

Achievements.Name: Blind Luck
Achievements.Description: Kill 25 enemies using blind fire.

Achievements.Name: Second Amendment
Achievements.Description: Kill at least one enemy with every available gun.

Achievements.Name: Say "No" to Pots
Achievements.Description: Shoot 30 potted plants.

Achievements.Name: Fire Hazard
Achievements.Description: Shoot and destroy 30 fire extinguishers.

Achievements.Name: Uncovered
Achievements.Description: Destroy 20 destructible cover objects.

Achievements.Name: Boom.
Achievements.Description: Blow up 50 explosive objects.

Achievements.Name: No Pain, No Gain
Achievements.Description: Kill an enemy with an explosive that also damages you.

Achievements.Name: Maxx Karnage
Achievements.Description: Collect 20 Hazard pickups.

Achievements.Name: Shield Master
Achievements.Description: Collect 20 Master Shield pickups.

Achievements.Name: Just a Flesh Wound
Achievements.Description: Complete a level without dying.

Achievements.Name: Hazard Avoider
Achievements.Description: Complete the game on the Minor Hazard difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: Pseudo-Hazard
Achievements.Description: Complete the game on the Major Hazard difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: Hazard Master
Achievements.Description: Complete the game on the Maximum Hazard difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: ...Where Credit is Due
Achievements.Description: Watch the credits from beginning to end.

Achievements.Name: Multiplayer Master!
Achievements.Description: "What? No multiplayer? Sigh. Well...not like we can take the achievement back NOW...."

Achievements.Name: Disco is Dead
Achievements.Description: Defeat Sonny Tang. "Sonny, YOUR ass is kicked!"

Achievements.Name: Stung
Achievements.Description: Defeat Sting Sniperscope. "Your present ends now."

Achievements.Name: Housing Crisis
Achievements.Description: Escape from Dexter's mansion. "I gotta get me a house like THAT!"

Achievements.Name: Talk!
Achievements.Description: "What do you mean the interrogation feature was cut?!? Here...just take the achievement."

Achievements.Name: Head Cheese
Achievements.Description: Kill all butcher shop enemies with headshots. "You're not PAYING for ammo. Feel free to use more."

Achievements.Name: Bedlam Basher
Achievements.Description: Kill a Bandit from behind with a melee attack. "Good for you. Coward."

Achievements.Name: Draw
Achievements.Description: Get 50 Dual-Wield Six-Shooter kills. "Now all we need is the spaghetti..."

Achievements.Name: Russian to the Finish
Achievements.Description: Defeat General Neutronov. "From Hazard, With Love."

Achievements.Name: Deja-Vu
Achievements.Description: Defeat Sting Sniperscope again in Level 3. "Your present ends now. Again."

Achievements.Name: Your Turn
Achievements.Description: Defeat Altos Tratus. "Forecast for the next level: no more clouds."

Achievements.Name: Meat Your Maker
Achievements.Description: Blast all hanging beef. "Udder destruction? Steaking a claim? Beating your...I can go on all day."

Achievements.Name: Well, I Heard them Scream
Achievements.Description: Get 50 Plasma Rifle kills. "Plasma rifles. They're not just for Space Marines anymore."

Achievements.Name: Dances with Guns
Achievements.Description: Don't let any dance bots die in Level 2. "Do dancing robots dream of disco sheep?"

Achievements.Name: Tramm Ride
Achievements.Description: Defeat the Tentacle Beast of Tramm. "One-two shot right to the tentacles."

Achievements.Name: Death Hazard
Achievements.Description: Score 20 single-shot Zombie kills. "Don't these things usually hang out in shopping malls?"

Achievements.Name: Pure Energy
Achievements.Description: Get 50 Energy Pistol kills. "Blaster? I hardly know 'er!"

Achievements.Name: Deja-Vu (All Over Again)
Achievements.Description: Defeat Sting Sniperscore yet AGAIN in Level 7. "I. Have had. Enough. Of YOU!!"

Achievements.Name: Observe the Grenade
Achievements.Description: Kill three Testers with one grenade launcher shot. "Test the grenades: check!"

Achievements.Name: Beat the Snot out of Wellesley
Achievements.Description: Defeat Wally Wellesley. "Like I said..."

Achievements.Name: Meet Quentin.
Achievements.Description: Meet Quentin. "DUDE!!!!!"
